## 2. Color Tokens

```css
/* Map these in tailwind.config.ts and src/styles/tokens.css */

--color-bg:           {{PRIMARY_COLOR}};   /* Page background */
--color-surface:      [slightly lighter];   /* Card / elevated surface */
--color-border:       [subtle line color];

--color-primary:      [main text color];
--color-text:         [body text, slightly muted];
--color-text-muted:   [secondary text];

--color-accent:       {{ACCENT_COLOR}};    /* Primary CTA, highlights */
--color-accent-2:     [secondary accent];  /* Optional: hover states */

--color-success:      #22C55E;
--color-danger:       #EF4444;
```

{{FIGMA_COLORS_SECTION}}

**Rules:**
- NEVER hardcode hex values in components
- NEVER use Tailwind arbitrary color values (`bg-[#hex]`)
- ALWAYS use token name (e.g. `bg-accent`, `text-primary`)

